[{"id":"95c049674c53e497c0e453b78ea33b1e","from":"LinkedIn Talent Solutions","from_email":"linkedin@e.linkedin.com","to":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","to_list":[{"name":"jeeproject@yahoo.com","email":"jeeproject@yahoo.com"}],"cc_list":[],"subject":"Reminder: 50% off a LinkedIn job post","date":"2015-10-28T08:13:51.000Z","formatted_date":"Oct 28, 2015","formatted_time":"8:13 AM","body":"For a limited time, get 50% off.\n\nLinkedIn\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-logo.png]https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYWUY&_ei_=Er69bEUx7PM3fRCKxRzD0TqsPqUSqugKX51ShAlaiiTcGxvwKPvquNImXb1NTQDMtq8_sNTNPlvcgbaVZu0Wfci4SzwXRkVVUydetwANh_jRUs-W35mORspwkZUtry_D19cp0cv1S5YCr11q1_GGexMPCNnNgZKtMrRa4x9rU7owAIwxSzhqjnZ1RD15tHknDA2oynZR9IMvSgkeLaF_ElTsmpXEYdZkVqAbkErI1RppWv7vguYSw58FfIJUEUUKCkS7yXKP3Zx--E4WLaOTkVMVXcUfi2g3yDxhdcR79es8EH0OtZrEoq9hFrUeNMmAh3Y.\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-color-bar.png]\n\nLet's find your\nnext great hire. For a limited time, get 50% off.\n\n\u00a0\n\nPost\u00a0a\u00a0job\n[https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYWYY&_ei_=Er69bEUx7PM3fRCKxRzD0TqsPqUSqugKX51ShAlaiiTcGxvwKPvquNImXb1NTQDMtq8_sNTNPlvcgbaVZu0Wfci4SzwXRkVVUydetwANh_jRUs-W35mORspwkZUtry_D10_-UsHHvHzzwTPnX-xu-QraFqlrP8nO-m7S2ylGOP-fBrM7lOwf-w6L7wVe8vjujCz717ITwE_26KN3B4Voe2b7i6bQWBKCo5atSVrB5F6AseOeN-LLZ13m3TMFB67Num3OJIi7HYg0wEpBD3sCViqnjm3wE_X_ID2sV_VTLY8kPnmqx-VqOn76uYC1Jr68aQv9lJLy1EvcAv7FqV2FtdjC7TD_OjC2bP-E6RuDLalh7eYE2BQ.]\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-three-columns-1-globe.png]\nUnbeatable reach Get access to 380 Million LinkedIn members, the world's largest\ntalent pool.\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-three-columns-2-thumb.png]\nQuality candidates Automatically show your job to members who are a great match.\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/flagship-ll-three-columns-3.png]\nApplicants guaranteed We guarantee you'll get at least 10 applicants or your\nmoney back.*\n\n\u00a0\n\n\u201cPosting on LinkedIn is fast and easy. Always quality candidates.\u201d \u2013 Kenyah\nFerguson, President, DMC Dallas\n\n\u00a0\n\nHow we help you find top talent\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-1.jpg]\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-1.jpg]\nProfile matches With every job post, you get a list of members who could be a\ngreat for your role \u2014 plus 5 free InMails to message them directly.\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-2.jpg]\nSmart targeting We'll share your job with members who match what you're looking\nfor \u2014 even if they're not actively looking for a new role.\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-2.jpg]\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-3.jpg]\n\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-how-3.jpg]\nEasy tracking Filter your applicants, take notes, then share them with your team\n\u2014 all without leaving LinkedIn.\n\n\u00a0\n\nTrusted by thousands of companies: Amazon - Sale Force - Apple\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-logo-1.png]Sony\n- Walmart\n[https://static.cdn.responsys.net/i5/responsysimages/content/linkedin/ppd-logo-2.png]\n\n\u00a0\n\nGet started now.\n\nPost\u00a0a\u00a0job\n[https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYWYY&_ei_=Er69bEUx7PM3fRCKxRzD0TqsPqUSqugKX51ShAlaiiTcGxvwKPvquNImXb1NTQDMtq8_sNTNPlvcgbaVZu0Wfci4SzwXRkVVUydetwANh_jRUs-W35mORspwkZUtry_D10_-UsHHvHzzwTPnX-xu-QraFqlrP8nO-m7S2ylGOP-fBrM7lOwf-w6L7wVe8vjujCz717ITwE_26KN3B4Voe2b7i6bQWBKCo5atSVrB5F6AseOeN-LLZ13m3TMFB67Num3OJIi7HYg0wEpBD3sCViqnjm3wE_X_ID2sV_VTLY8kPnmqx-VqOn76uYC1Jr68aQv9lJLy1EvcAv7FqV2FtdjC7TD_OjC2bP-E6RuDLalh7eYE2BQ.]\n\nFor a limited time, get 50% off.\n\n*LINKEDIN JOBS APPLICANTS GUARANTEE: Subject to the conditions outlined below,\nLinkedIn will refund the cost of one 30-day job post (\"Job Post\") on LinkedIn's\nsite that does not receive 10 or more applications through the LinkedIn site, so\nlong as the LinkedIn member creating the Job Post follows the following three\nsteps and abides by the additional terms set forth below:\n\nThree Steps:\n 1. The Job Post must contain a complete job description - including \"Skills\"\n    and \"Company Description\";\n 2. The Job Post must use a standardized Job Title selected from the drop-down\n    suggestions on the Job posting page; and\n 3. The Job Post must be for a standardized Company selected from the drop-down\n    suggestions on the Job posting page.\n\nAdditional Terms and Conditions:\n * Offer is not transferable\n * 50% off job offer expires on November 10 2015\n * Guarantee only applies to single Job posts, purchased individually or with\n   credits. Corporate Job Slots are not eligible for the refund.\n * Only one refund will be provided per LinkedIn member.\n * The Job Post must accept applications on LinkedIn.\n * The Job Post must be available on LinkedIn for at least 30 days and have\n   expired before applications will be counted.\n * Participants eligible for a refund will be contacted through email with\n   instructions to redeem the refund.\n * Offer may be revoked at any time, for any reason by LinkedIn.\n * Offer is void where prohibited or restricted by law.\n\nIf you need assistance or have questions, please contact LinkedIn Customer\nService\n[https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYWDY&_ei_=EolaGGF4SNMvxFF7Kuc