 instructions to redeem the refund.</li>\n                        <li>Offer may be revoked at any time, for any reason by LinkedIn.</li>\n                        <li>Offer is void where prohibited or restricted by law.</li>\n                        </ul>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\nIf you need assistance or have questions, please contact <a href=\"https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYWDY&_ei_=EolaGGF4SNMvxFF7KucKuWPn4BDulVhw2Oi43yLe_FD35n5ytJr94_eHhmQiAUyDFPbi-HBLPRXYnA0Vohfq41DAmXWmS5h0zGhhKZOAjQipZbPUDQROkjTVKSND9WeZ_DObrCLueNYS3G8PaG3ao8Shy0zqe_6MkZ_28RgFBxapaPUJiY3qDWxDuYr69FO-PdJVvRayWTvFdDaLTQ1_47bdSEjeHxYYMID_kE1Sa-QU22s-CHAFBElOLCGSp_9Nb2QEEvaqfrOJYg.\" rilt=\"HELP_ENGLISH\" style=\"color:#006699;\">LinkedIn Customer Service</a>.\n            <br />\nThis is an occasional email to help you get the most out of LinkedIn. <a href=\"https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYYSY&_ei_=EolaGGF4SNMvxFF7KucKuWPn4BDulVhw2Oi43yLe_FD35n5ytJr94_eHhmQiAUyDFPbi-HBLPRXYnA0Vohfq41DAmXWmS5h0zGhhKZOAjQipZbPUDQROkjTVKSND9WeZ_DObrCLueNYS3G8PaG3ao8Shy0zqe_6MkZ_28RgFBxapaPUJiY3qDWxDuYr69FO-PbGnnVyC3bx_2zM1q3iJT6gdNYmFDgJJwnUTW5cWSaw2BhnLucp1gbhw0qf45QyRo1wB6gUHbO6Lil9Hv-vLMIyupT42nPND5tmjXRmAyfha-xm6Nrcypi1CvPik8r5b0STZEXSozlNmeMnecwmINTAFfo6ydMfufqbXmu75Fr-EqKaDNMLlpL52V9hnCTEi.\" rilt=\"UNSUB\" style=\"color:#006699;\">Unsubscribe</a>.\n\t\t\t<br />\nThis email was intended for Jeffrey Epstein &#40;--&#41;. <a href=\"https://e.linkedin.com/pub/cc?_ri_=X0Gzc2X%3DYQpglLjHJlYQGn4hXzb2lNww8YmXvgwDXzfL6JzfbdPM6RU2pza7rLLv1BesjrDBIuiGVXtpKX%3DWBYYUY&_ei_=EolaGGF4SNMvxFF7KucKuWPn4BDulVhw2Oi43yLe_FD35n5ytJr94_eHhmQiAUyDFPbi-HBLPRXYnA0Vohfq41DAmXWmS5h0zGhhKZOAjQipZbPUDQROkjTVKSND9WeZ_DObrCLueNYS3G8PaG3ao8Shy0zqe_6MkZ_28RgFBxapaPUJiY3qDWxDuYr69FO-PdJVvRayWTvFdDaLTQ1_47bdSEjeHxYYMID_kE1Sa-QU22s-CHAFBElOLCGSp_9Nb2QEEvaqfr